Format 35
Input stdclass.inc

NoStyle Chapter
NoCounter chapter
NoStyle Chapter*

SecNumDepth             3
TocDepth                3


ClassOptions
	PageStyle     empty|plain|outer|headings|myheadings|uheadings|myuheadings
End


Style Part
	Align                 Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
	TocLevel 0
End


Style Part*
	Align                 Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
End
